<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Test: Percentage height and width on replaced content</title>
        <link rel="author" title="Microsoft" href="http://www.microsoft.com/" />
        <link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/visudet.html#the-width-property" />
        <meta name="flags" content="HTMLonly invalid" />
        <meta name="assert" content="Verify percentage based width and height on replaced content." />
        <style type="text/css">
            #d1
            {
                width: 200px;
                height: 200px;
                border: solid 1px black;
            }
            iframe
            {
                width: 50%;
                height: 50%;
                border: solid 1px blue;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div id="d1">
            <iframe></iframe>
        </div>
        <p>Test passes if a blue bordered box is in the top/left corner of the container.</p>
    </body>
</html>